{
  "texts": [
    "Modeling such algorithm should thus define some type of data it has access to.",
    "The variety of input data used by commercial recommender systems is part of the domain of business secrecy such that little is known about which input data are really used.",
    "We will here select two broad categories of data that are likely to be used by commercial recommenders (cf.",
    "Xu & Yang 2012; Huszár et al. 2022):",
    "• Sentiment analysis: the negative or positive/neutral nature of a tweets, as well as the proportion of negative content retweeted by the user in the past."
  ]
}